                     <interp inst="t17920704-5-defend105" type="age" value="26"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for, <rs id="t17920704-5-off25" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17920704-5-off25" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920704-5-off25" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he on the <rs id="t17920704-5-cd26" type="crimeDate">11th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920704-5-off25 t17920704-5-cd26"></join> last falsely and feloniously did make, forge, and counterfeit, and cause and procure to be falsely made, forged, and counterfeited, and did willingly act and assist in the false making, forging, and counterfeiting a certain order for payment of money, dated the 11th of April, 1792, with the name of 
                     <persName id="t17920704-5-person106">
                        George
                         Hardinge
